      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为这个工业IoT场景设计一个状态图。起点是IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController，它进入一个Lobby等待状态。整个流程是主持人驱动的问答游戏机制。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "Lobby"
