      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以ActuatorController先进入Lobby。那从Lobby怎么触发游戏开始？需要明确触发条件吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Lobby",
        "GameStarted"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，主持人点击开始后，Lobby转移到GameStarted状态。然后需要初始化题目，进入QuestionPrep准备状态。接着主持人展示题目，转移到QuestionActive。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Lobby",
        "GameStarted",
        "QuestionPrep",
        "QuestionActive",
        "Host Starts",
        "Init Question",
        "Host Shows"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把这几个状态和转移加进去了。现在处理玩家抢答的逻辑——玩家按下抢答器后应该进入AnswerValidation验证状态，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "QuestionActive",
        "AnswerValidation",
        "Player Buzzes"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。验证结果分两种：答对了回到QuestionPrep准备下一题，答错了返回QuestionActive让其他人继续抢答。另外主持人可以随时结束游戏，从QuestionPrep直接跳到GameOver。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AnswerValidation",
        "QuestionPrep",
        "QuestionActive",
        "GameOver",
        "Correct Answer",
        "Wrong Answer",
        "Host Ends"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
