      "utterance": "完成了。我检查一下：ActuatorController起始于Lobby，经Host Starts到GameStarted，然后Init Question到QuestionPrep，Host Shows到QuestionActive，Player Buzzes触发AnswerValidation，正确回QuestionPrep，错误回QuestionActive，Host Ends到GameOver，最终到PLC_Logic。结构完整。",
